n of a powerful little alien that you may or may not have stolen/liberated from the evil Empire. As the Empire closes in, you'll need to find a way to balance your ship's management with the onslaught of attacks. Do you have what it takes to survive?"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "1324311035174797", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984472_1324311038508130_2610060411856834928_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Ne_wahpCXGQQ7kNvgGLpGx-&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDpg_7Ev5V_IxsJYfNMw2CocsYnt5RpmrGTa45v03TMdA&oe=670CF6F8"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Portrait.png", "id": "1021944422558335", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031612_1021944425891668_3460677483354056217_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YNjxx7CLrUMQ7kNvgGy4UTi&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA_nnPzE-0y_SBJyUHLQJdLFsJ75v_qZK9K1lySlknE7w&oe=670CF6FE"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Square.png", "id": "998366967853309", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031369_998366971186642_4701792016341896524_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=V3lnBRInQJ0Q7kNvgHEMW-j&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDAdQYQAXcPnTejViyfTK4TPiyjGT2UEZvTJPekCnjCxQ&oe=670D0443"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "973425620588096", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86610716_973425627254762_5218087471640407679_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7UOr781QGJMQ7kNvgElCzPz&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAXnwYse43h2ANX2eO_WIU7TizHqNZN7y5wC3IZFSf2Dw&oe=670D1D81"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Landscape.png", "id": "822780949101586", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75557065_822780952434919_8573226718553